        <script type="text/javascript">
            function pageLoad() {
                var qs = getQueryStrings();
                if (window.location.href.indexOf("www.kemet.com") > -1) {
                    $("#suiteBar").hide();
                    $("#s4-ribbonrow").hide();
		    	
                }
                var myParam = qs["pagetype"];
                if (myParam == "distributor") {
                    $(".header").hide();
                    $(".links").hide();
                    $(".footer").hide();
                    $("#suiteBar").hide();
                    $("#s4-ribbonrow").hide();
                    $('body').addClass("DistributorBody");
                    if (window.location.href.indexOf("/Products") > -1 || window.location.href.indexOf("/RecentProducts") > -1) {
                    }
                    else {
                        $('#main_container').css('float', 'left');
                    }
                }


            }

            function getQueryStrings() {
                var assoc = {};
                var decode = function (s) { return decodeURIComponent(s.replace(/\+/g, " ")); };
                var queryString = location.search.substring(1);
                var keyValues = queryString.split('&');

                for (var i in keyValues) {
                    var key = keyValues[i].split('=');
                    if (key.length > 1) {
                        assoc[decode(key[0]).toLowerCase()] = decode(key[1].toLowerCase());
                    }
                }

                return assoc;
            }
        </script>
